00:00:04.802 --> 00:00:06.041
over sharing my intrusive

00:00:06.042 --> 00:00:08.761
inner monologue with strangers who didn't ask to hear it.

00:00:08.762 --> 00:00:09.761
So from today, day 1,

00:00:09.762 --> 00:00:11.161
I started writing my thoughts down.

00:00:11.162 --> 00:00:12.281
Totally radical concept

00:00:12.282 --> 00:00:15.641
