00:00:19.642 --> 00:00:20.481
And in the second week,

00:00:20.482 --> 00:00:23.561
I thought I might treat myself and find a cute new show on Netflix.

00:00:23.562 --> 00:00:25.921
It wasn't even a baby reindeer.

00:00:25.922 --> 00:00:28.521
When that plan backfired, I thought I'd try some light reading instead

00:00:28.522 --> 00:00:30.521
